.TH std::ranges::count,std::ranges::count_if 3 "2021.11.17" "http://cppreference.com" "C++ Standard Libary"
.SH NAME
std::ranges::count,std::ranges::count_if \- std::ranges::count,std::ranges::count_if

.SH Synopsis
   Defined in header <algorithm>
   Call signature
